Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Drought hits farmers
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xqh9
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 17 Aug 1986
Government set to bail out farmers after worst drought for decades devastates crops and livestock. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less